  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/e3cba87a9aa51208f1fe50024e3ea4ed.poster.avif?t=1774278509\" width=620 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/e3cba87a9aa51208f1fe50024e3ea4ed.webm?t=1774278509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the tallest tower!</h2>Find and craft the best possible blocks and stack them to build the tallest and the prettier tower before the other team!<br>Zigglox is a <strong>multiplayer online game</strong> that plays from 4 to 8 players confronting a team versus another.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/86e5697620df66fc55ecbc1741fa80a3.poster.avif?t=1774278509\" width=620 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/86e5697620df66fc55ecbc1741fa80a3.webm?t=1774278509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Run, jump, carry, craft, build and kick you ennemies out!</h2>Zigglox plays with a controller or a keyboard. The main objective is to stack more colored bricks than your opponents to <strong>get more points</strong>.<br>Be careful though... Some colored blocks stacked together can result in <strong>combos</strong>!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/3e07cd1c19be0ab045504dd1df27977e.poster.avif?t=1774278509\" width=620 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/3e07cd1c19be0ab045504dd1df27977e.webm?t=1774278509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Show no mercy!</h2>Guide yourself across the map by crafting <strong>special combos</strong>. Use combinations to help with your <strong>strategy</strong>, but beware, some combos might end in dynamite!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some special combos:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/91318495ca66b0ac353c6c94b446562f.avif?t=1774278509\" width=620 height=302 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/48539ed05a1f89ea922994268aa340c1.poster.avif?t=1774278509\" width=620 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/48539ed05a1f89ea922994268aa340c1.webm?t=1774278509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online multiplayer game</h2>Play with friends... Or not! Create games all around the world, join friends, or join random games. The more Zigglox there are, t<strong>he taller the tower will be</strong>!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/9c2ac983e0a43ebd7c2161f601909e11.poster.avif?t=1774278509\" width=620 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514880/extras/9c2ac983e0a43ebd7c2161f601909e11.webm?t=1774278509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Final game (later 2022) content:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>HOST:</strong> play with your friends creating a private room</li><li><strong>TUTORIAL:</strong> Hang out in the blocks factory and learn how to play</li><li><strong>7 MAPS</strong></li><li><strong>10+ SKINS</strong></li><li><strong>10+ SPECIAL COMBOS</strong></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2>Zigglox have been made by a very small team, Herael and Jeremiam, two french gamedev that enjoyed creating Zigglox :)",
